[The UK continues its efforts to destroy the disease. However, for whatever
reason, they have yet to be able to destroy infected animals within 24
hours of diagnosis. This appears to be critical to eliminating the disease.
This continued tailing of the disease, and perhaps a new upswing as the
country approaches winter, does not indicate that there is control of the
disease. ­ Mod.TG
